text: Tatyana Mudritskaya (born 17 January 1985 in Mogilev-Podolskiy, Ukraine) is a Kazakhstani female volleyball player. She is a member of the Kazakhstan women's national volleyball team, and played for Schweriner SC in 2014. She was part of the Kazakhstani national team at the 2014 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship in Italy. ==Clubs== * 1999-2005 Khimvolokno * 2005-2007 Galatasaray, Turkey. * 2007-2008 Rakhat, Kazakhstan. * 2009 AEL, Limassol, Cyprus * 2011-2013 Anorthosis, Cyprus * 2014 Schweriner SC ==References== ==External links == * FIVB profile Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani women's volleyball players Category:People from Mohyliv- Podilskyi
